@startuml
title UC-2 비상 상황 자동 해제

actor "Crash Detection System / Airbag Control Unit" as CDS
actor "Cluster / HMI System" as HMI
boundary "Crash Signal Interface" as CSI
control "ChildLockController" as CLC
entity "ChildLockState" as CLS
boundary "Rear Door Module Interface" as RDMI
boundary "Door Panel Interface" as DPI

CDS -> CSI : crashDetected()
activate CSI

CSI -> CLC : emergencyUnlockRequest()
activate CLC

CLC -> CLS : getState()
activate CLS
CLS --> CLC : childLockState
deactivate CLS

alt 차일드락 ON 상태

    CLC -> RDMI : applyChildLockState(OFF)
    activate RDMI
    RDMI --> CLC : stateApplied
    deactivate RDMI

    CLC -> CLS : setState(OFF)
    activate CLS
    CLS --> CLC : stateUpdated
    deactivate CLS

    ref over CLC, DPI
      UC-3 차일드락 상태 표시 제공
    end ref

    ref over CLC, HMI
      UC-4 시스템 개입 상황 알림 제공
    end ref

else 차일드락 이미 OFF

    note right of CLC
      상태 변경 없음
    end note

end

deactivate CLC
deactivate CSI
@enduml
